Package Util

Class RepositoryGetter

java.lang.Object
Util.RepositoryGetter
public class RepositoryGetter extends Object
Utility class for retrieving singleton instances of various repositories. Each method provides a way to access the singleton instance of a repository, ensuring centralized and consistent access to data storage.
